- "blooms" is a metaphorical term used here to represent the titles of the reports.;
- "cultivated" is metaphorically referring to the act of authoring or creating reports.;

sql:
SELECT SUM(expected_deaths) AS total_expected_deaths
FROM mortality_data
WHERE age_distribution_deaths > (SELECT AVG(age_distribution_deaths) FROM mortality_data);

